Heaven’s gate has opened, we’ve found a way to travel to the evangelic realm to uncover the secrets that lay within. At the heart of this mysterious world lies the city of Elysia, once called paradise, ravaged through war and famine. With lost sols wandering about, the first to unlock the gate will decide the fate of Elysia.
